"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"***一个由开发者、企业家、艺术家和加密爱好者组成的充满活力的社区描绘了以太坊区块链的未来，因为它经历了前所未有的增长。以太坊：无限花园是一部以人物为导向的纪录片，讲述了建立一个新世界的挑战和回报。***\\n\\n**更新：该活动已正式结束。**\\n\\n哇！我们对社区的支持感到震惊。在 3 天内，我们超越了我们的目标。\\n\\n为电影的制作预算筹集了 984.16 ETH。\\n\\n31\\\\.08 ETH 到 Gitcoin 赠款。\\n\\n20\\\\.72 ETH 到 CarbonFund.org。\\n\\n感谢所有做出贡献的人，并祝贺我们的新制作人。请务必加入电影的私人[Discord](https://discord.gg/U7dA59fvPN)，我们将在那里发布有关电影的更新。\\n\\n对于贡献者，请填写下面的表格，根据您的捐赠等级获得积分。如果提交仇恨或攻击性语言，我们保留拒绝信用的权利。\\n\\n加入我们的以太坊：无限花园的制作，并参与这个开创性的实验，成为第一部使用 NFT 筹款的纪录片。\\n\\n我们正在与[pppleasr 合作](https://twitter.com/pplpleasr1)，放弃一系列与电影中的银幕字幕相关的无限花园 NFT。所有贡献者都可以访问电影的私人 Discord 聊天。查看下面的奖励等级。\\n\\n我们的众筹将于 7 月 16 日星期五太平洋夏令时间下午 3 点/美国东部时间下午 6 点结束。\\n\\n![](https://ethereumfilm.mirror.xyz/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.mirror-media.xyz%2Fpublication-images%2F8f48140b-f332-4d9c-9d61-353867e63d2e.jpeg&w=3840&q=90)\\n\\n### 运动\\n\\n我们正着手制作第一部长篇以太坊纪录片！\\n\\n去年春天，我们与 Vitalik Buterin 和 Aya Miyaguchi 建立了独家拍摄关系。我们现在正在积极地与许多以太坊最具创新性的社区成员进行交流和交谈。\\n\\n作为经验丰富的独立电影制作人，我们了解通过传统电影融资方式筹集资金的挑战。通过 Mirror 筹款使我们能够保持电影的创意愿景，同时快速增加制作以实时捕捉这个不断发展的故事。\\n\\n最重要的是，它让我们有机会让社区参与这部电影的制作。\\n\\n赞助人讲台\\n\\n当众筹结束时，前三名支持者将获得一个独特的 NFT。通过贡献带头并成为前三名的支持者。\\n\\n剩余时间\\n\\n如果在最后 15 分钟内做出贡献并更改了领奖台位置，则时间将重置为 15 分钟。\\n\\n## 奖励等级\\n\\n### 花园层\\n\\n顶级贡献者将根据他们在众筹排行榜中的排名获得独家 NFT 和银幕电影学分。\\n\\n**第一名**\\n\\n* 电影中的“执行制片人”功劳\\n* 1/1“执行园丁”无限花园海报NFT空投，以你的名字为“执行制作人”\\n\\n**第二名**\\n\\n* 电影中的“联合执行制片人”功劳\\n* 1/1“联合执行园丁”无限花园NFT空投，以你的名字为“联合执行制片人”\\n\\n**第三名**\\n\\n* 电影中的“特约制片人”功劳\\n* 1/1“贡献园丁”无限花园NFT空投，以你的名字为“贡献制作人”\\n\\n**支持者 4-20**\\n\\n支持者 4–20\\n\\n* Your name included in the “Infinite Thanks” section in the film's credits, reserved only for leaderboard backers 4-20\\n* Airdrop of 1/17 \\\"Infinite Thanks\\\" Infinite Garden Poster NFT\\n\\n### Bloom Tier\\n\\nUnlocked by purchasing the Bloom NFT for 1 ETH.\\n\\n* Infinite Garden Bloom NFT\\n* Your name included in the “Special Thanks” section in the the film's credits\\n* All items from Seed Tier\\n\\n### Sprout Tier\\n\\nTier available to contributions above .5 ETH.\\n\\n* Your name included in the \\\"Mirror.xyz Crowdfund Backer\\\" section in the film's credits\\n* All items from Seed Tier\\n\\n### Seed Tier\\n\\nTier available to all contributors.\\n\\n* Mention in the acknowledgments on the film's website\\n* Access to a private [Discord](https://discord.gg/U7dA59fvPN) chat where we’ll share periodic updates on the film and filmmaking process.\\n\\n### Fundraising Split\\n\\n* 95% - Film’s Production Budget\\n* 2% - Carbon Offset through donation to Carbonfund.org\\n* 3% - Gitcoin Grants to support open-source Ethereum projects\\n\\nAll proceeds distributed to the film’s production budget will go directly towards the hard costs of the making of the film.\\n\\n*Please note:*\\n\\n*In order to receive your credit in the film or on the website, you must join our [Discord](https://discord.gg/U7dA59fvPN) server to receive directions about how to link your name to your contribution address.*\\n\\n*Your contribution does not provide you with creative control or ownership of the film.*\\n\\n*$INFINITE tokens should only be used to access the private Discord chat. We discourage the resale or speculation of this token.*\\n\\n*The film team has the right to return funds if we believe the patron’s values are misaligned with the project.*\\n\\n### About the film\\n\\nWhat if we could create a world where every transaction was decentralized? Where buying art, voting, fundraising, and even social media were not controlled by a central company or intermediary, but rather an open-source, community-run network where code runs without interference. In 2013 Vitalik Buterin, an 18-year-old Bitcoin enthusiast and writer proposed the tools to make that future possible. Less than a decade later, thousands of developers have contributed to building the Ethereum ecosystem: a technology that enables decentralized applications, including but not limited to money. For many, [Ethereum is building the internet of value](https://www.coindesk.com/ethereum-building-internet-of-value).\\n\\nBut as Ethereum grows in size and popularity, it faces mounting pressure from cutting-edge competitors, hype markets, and criticisms for its scalability and energy consumption. Spearheaded by a global team of researchers and developers, a push to upgrade the platform could address the criticisms and unlock the technology's full potential... or it could derail the still-budding $300 billion network.\\n\\nFollowing the high-stakes journey to upgrade the platform, ETHEREUM: THE INFINITE GARDEN is a feature-length documentary film that explores the innovative real-world applications of the Ethereum blockchain, the die-hard community of enthusiasts and developers, and its creator, Vitalik Buterin, whose vision for the internet has the potential to change the world.\\n\\n### The Infinite Garden\\n\\nIn this film, we approach Ethereum as an “infinite garden.” Instead of thinking of Ethereum as a machine controlled by a central brain, we see it as a decentralized ecosystem with soil, plants, and insects that need to be cared for in order to grow.\\n\\nThe idea of the infinite garden was conceptualized by Aya Miyaguchi, the executive director of the Ethereum Foundation. She was inspired by James P. Carse’s book *Finite and Infinite Games*. The following basic principles are at its core:\\n\\n* A finite game is played for the purpose of winning; An infinite game is played for the purpose of continuing the play\\n* The rules of finite games may not change; the rules of infinite games must change\\n* Finite players play within boundaries; Infinite players play without boundaries\\n* Finite players are serious; Infinite players are playful\\n* Finite players play to win titles; Infinite players have nothing but their names\\n* A finite player plays to be powerful; an infinite player plays with strength\\n* Finite players are theatrical; infinite players are dramatic\\n* A finite player consumes time; an infinite player generates time\\n* The finite players aims to win eternal life; the infinite player aims for eternal birth\\n\\nThose who tend to the seeds they plant in the Ethereum garden can nurture and empower the ecosystem, but can also harm it. For a crypto culture to remain equitable, decentralized, and sustainable, it must be tended to carefully. ETHEREUM: THE INFINITE GARDEN will introduce us to these early “gardeners” of the platform as they face the mounting pressures and challenges of the growing ecosystem.\\n\\n### Director's Statement\\n\\nAs a kid, I grew up in a strictly open-source household. My dad’s radical adoration of Linux introduced me to the potential of community-led technology (and mind blowing internet [weirdness](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-5x5OXfe9KY)) before I was even in grade school. Today, I feel that same excitement my dad once felt, but for Ethereum and the unique community that powers it.\\n\\n![](https://ethereumfilm.mirror.xyz/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.mirror-media.xyz%2Fpublication-images%2Fd4406f2a-503f-46ec-ba6b-89db89fdd8df.jpeg&w=3840&q=90)\\n\\nMy hope is to make Ethereum accessible and understandable to the world. By highlighting diverse stories from the global network of developers, founders, and end-users, we can create an emotional and human record of Ethereum’s journey. From the inspiring Axie Infinity gamers in the Philippines supporting their families during COVID to the tireless developers making Proof of Stake possible, there already is a bountiful garden to explore.\\n\\n三十年后，当我们的孩子从一个由可编程区块链技术驱动的世界回首时，他们会想知道背后是谁，他们面临哪些挑战，他们做出了哪些牺牲。与其用零散的记忆和对“ [Just Keep Chugging](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yvr0xYeV94M) ”模因的糟糕解释让他们感到厌烦，不如给他们以太坊：无限花园。\\n\\n*-扎克·英格拉西，导演*\\n\\n![](https://ethereumfilm.mirror.xyz/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.mirror-media.xyz%2Fpublication-images%2Fed408928-e082-4606-ad6c-f393ec2fb501.jpeg&w=3840&q=90)\\n\\n### 预计时间表\\n\\n* 2021 年春夏：开发与铸造\\n* 2021 年夏季至 2022 年冬季：基本摄影\\n* 2022 年春季：开始\\n* 2022 年夏季：粗剪\\n* 2022 年秋季：锁定图片\\n* 2023 年冬季：电影节首映/发布\\n\\n### NFT 艺术家的笔记\\n\\n> 这件作品让我兴奋，因为它可能是第一批兼作电影海报的 NFT 之一，代表了社区所相信的很多东西。它反映了我对“无限花园”的解释，并使用了交叉引用主要内容的调色板来自以太坊网站的插图以及我之前的作品。我发现自己处于 NFT、DAO 和 DeFi 交叉点的独特位置，我绝对不想将这种关注视为理所当然。我感到有责任以积极和雄辩的方式帮助传播对这些主题的认识，而这部纪录片无疑是朝着这个方向迈出的一步。\\n\\n*- pplpleasr，NFT 艺术家*\\n\\n**喜欢的人**\\n\\n![](https://ethereumfilm.mirror.xyz/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.mirror-media.xyz%2Fpublication-images%2Fd694da66-57b2-4903-b109-6d654d6f9a76.jpeg&w=640&q=90)\\n\\n[pppleasr](https://twitter.com/pplpleasr1)是一位[住](https://twitter.com/pplpleasr1)在纽约的多学科雪人。她作为数字演员的工作包括故事片（蝙蝠侠大战超人、神奇女侠、星际迷航）、商业广告和暴暴电影游戏中的效果视觉。2020年，pppleasr为Aave、Sushiswap、 Yearn、Poloniex 和其他 13 个知名品牌制作原创动画而走红。pppleasr 的作品风格受到动画电影、地下音乐场景、电子游戏以及中国和日本传统艺术的影响。灵感来自 Moebius 的艺术，它提供了 3D 元素被 2D 插图的错觉。\\n\\n### NFT音乐\\n\\n**过去的时光树**\\n\\n![](https://ethereumfilm.mirror.xyz/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.mirror-media.xyz%2Fpublication-images%2F71f66fba-5953-43a9-acd0-c7f8d438e8d1.jpeg&w=640&q=90)\\n\\n[Past Palms](https://twitter.com/PastPalms)是一家总部位于纽约的制作人，创作郁郁葱葱的音乐来为您的植物浇水。音乐旨在概括生活在一个灰色的、缺乏自然的城市的同时，被热带室内植物绿洲包围的感觉。\\n\\n### 关于纪录片团队\\n\\n![](https://ethereumfilm.mirror.xyz/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.mirror-media.xyz%2Fpublication-images%2F7584263a-391e-49fb-b5dd-db9ee9902ecc.jpeg&w=640&q=90)\\n\\n**克里斯·坦普尔和扎克·英格拉西**\\n\\n[扎克](https://twitter.com/zachingrasci)和[克里斯](https://twitter.com/christemple8)的英文电影导演，也是洛杉矶制作工作室[乐观](https://optimist.co/)的创始人。他们最著名的作品是执导纪录片[“一美元生活”](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ze72rpWp_Dg)，“[萨拉姆邻居](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W6SxPSZVD9o)”和[“北方五年”](https://vimeo.com/542843722)。他们的由Netflix公司、HBO、Hulu、国家和电影、电影、电视剧、电视剧等，并主要在节节上放映，包括翠贝卡、DOC NYC、Full Frame、AFI Docs、CPH:DOX、Mountainfilm等。他们最近的电影的《北方五年》也入杜邦-哥伦比亚街头新闻奖的决赛。电影作品有4个矮子奖、2个ADDY奖、1个ADDY奖、1个比奖和2个AV数字奖。乐观乐观主义者的工作工作帮助为发现金融权和教育工作电影的影响作用了已910 万美元。\\n\\n**Carrie Weprin - 制片人**\\n\\n![](https://ethereumfilm.mirror.xyz/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.mirror-media.xyz%2Fpublication-images%2Fcab63cea-b418-41ca-959d-3e33766760e4.jpeg&w=640&q=90)\\n\\n[Carrie Weprin](https://twitter.com/carrieannewep)是一位创意电影制片人，致力于创造性的非虚构故事讲述工艺。Carrie 曾为 A&E 电视网络、MTV 网络、谷歌、Facebook、纽约时报和 PBS 制作内容。作为独立制片人，Carrie 的作品包括获奖影片：Tough Love (2014, Full Frame FF)、The Growing Season (2016, DOCNYC) Blowin' Up (2018, Tribeca FF)、Sounds of Summer (2020, Camden IFF)。2020 年，她获得了圣丹斯创意制片人奖学金和影响合作伙伴制片人奖学金。Carrie 是由女性主导的制作公司“Once in a Blue”的联合创始人，她与丈夫、儿子、女儿和猫 Levon 在布鲁克林和 Catskills 之间分配时间。\\n\\n**珍娜凯利 - 制片人**\\n\\n![](https://ethereumfilm.mirror.xyz/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.mirror-media.xyz%2Fpublication-images%2Fb0510e77-3f67-4dd7-8b47-dfea5d8fe319.jpeg&w=1080&q=90)\\n\\n[珍娜](https://twitter.com/JennaMKelly)是纪录片《北方五年》的制片人，该纪录片于 2020 年全画幅首映，并获得了纽约市 DOC 和 Flickers 罗德岛电影节的评审团大奖。这部电影还入围了 2021 年杜邦-哥伦比亚杰出新闻奖的决赛。珍娜还制作了屡获殊荣的短纪录片《无证律师》，该纪录片将于 2021 年在 HBO 首映。她是纪录片制片人联盟的成员。她目前正在开发几部新的短片和专题纪录片和系列片。\\n\\n**谢琳达 - 联合制片人**\\n\\n![](https://ethereumfilm.mirror.xyz/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.mirror-media.xyz%2Fpublication-images%2F7af2f4ad-450c-4143-9116-d8e8f0a522ed.jpeg&w=750&q=90)\\n\\n[Linda](https://twitter.com/ljxie)是加密投资公司 Scalar Capital 的联合创始人。此前，她是 Coinbase 的早期员工和产品经理。她还是以太坊去中心化交易协议 0x 的顾问。Linda 一直是 SF Ethereum Developers meetup 的联合组织者，并且热衷于为加密编写教育内容。\\n\\n**傻先生 - 顾问**\\n\\n![](https://ethereumfilm.mirror.xyz/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.mirror-media.xyz%2Fpublication-images%2F75ec277e-d248-4937-91e3-eef219c95d1a.jpeg&w=828&q=90)\\n\\n前比特币资助者变成了以太坊爱好者和开发者。您在 Vitalik 的[合法性帖子中看到](https://vitalik.ca/general/2021/03/23/legitimacy.html)了愚蠢的先生。\\n\\n**摩根贝勒 - 顾问**\\n\\n![](https://ethereumfilm.mirror.xyz/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.mirror-media.xyz%2Fpublication-images%2F5173b53c-809b-4803-a6e8-444fe105cfad.jpeg&w=640&q=90)\\n\\n[摩根](https://twitter.com/beller)是衍生期风险投资基金 NFX 的普通合伙人。在此之前，摩根在安德森霍洛维茨的交易团队中工作。\",\"timestamp\":1639291032,\"title\":\"Ethereum: The Infinite Garden — Mirror\"},\"digest\":\"8fCOMrbUCkysCgemi-c-7M-dA4Ew2jtIBNZXZiS3sRM\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xc7c8Fa917D383cBc649ea2C6397A5ad9456F60C9\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"FHb0eHJUAvIWrBj3I1D-e5q4gj75xARO6BL8q6EPH4I\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"sl2IKnVQreN9qvoZI8LycFV9jYGDp3bCdwIbuHaFMg8\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"z15t6hauOoyJhxry3gwjGqaKiP7qypzKoXvW-LkJMFy9tzb5-XRqiY3rvO_v5b7Rtv7Fp5utkYOaHZly-S8axA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x2b05dde2e7f3878ff5e4ea977e922057a3fcaa06291145fed3024ae7324a5f2c1ede08eea19a779843c43283828065f130115443beadb6a424d0ca8a0bb30af01c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"FHb0eHJUAvIWrBj3I1D-e5q4gj75xARO6BL8q6EPH4I\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"sl2IKnVQreN9qvoZI8LycFV9jYGDp3bCdwIbuHaFMg8\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"8fCOMrbUCkysCgemi-c-7M-dA4Ew2jtIBNZXZiS3sRM\"}"